<template>
    <!-- Vue3组件中的模板结构中可以没有根标签 -->
    <Demo @hello="showHello" msg="你好啊" school="尚硅谷"/>
  </template>
  <script>
  import Demo from './components/Demo';
  export default {
    name:'App',
    components:{Demo},
    setup(props) {
      function showHello(){
        console.log('你好啊,你触发了hello事件')
      }
      return {
        showHello
      }
    }
  };
  </script>

  <style>
  </style>
